  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-02 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Full 13-factor assessment is included. The package decision is recorded as Accepted on the basis that uncertainty quantification was completed and most factors met or approached their required levels; however, two factors carry achievedLevel values strictly below requiredLevel, constituting an unresolved structural shortfall.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cou2-hemolysis-absolute",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cou2-cfd-hemolysis-acceptable",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/morrison-cfd-centrifugal-pump-v3",
